  "Description": {
    "English": "This <span class=\"name name-fuel\">antimatter-based fuel</span> is one of the few power sources capable of meeting the incredible energy requirements of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">starship hyperdrive</span>.<br><br>Secured within a robust housing, the cell is guaranteed paradox-free during FTL travel.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这个<span class=\"name name-fuel\">基于反物质的燃料</span>是极少数能够满足<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船超光速推进器</span>惊人要求的能量之一。<br><br>电池放置在固若金汤的外壳里，既安全又可以保证超光速旅行。",
    "TencentChinese": "这个<span class=\"name name-fuel\">基于反物质的燃料</span>是极少数能够满足<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船超光速推进器</span>惊人要求的能量之一。<br><br>这个细胞待在固若金汤的外壳里，既安全又可以保证超光速旅行。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-fuel\">反物質燃料</span>是少數能滿足<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船超空間驅動器</span>嚴苛能量需求的能量來源。<br><br>這種電池安置於堅固的容器中，能確保超光速旅行時不會產生悖論。"
  },
